data.description:
This charming ranch-style home has recently undergone stunning renovations, making it a fantastic opportunity for
anyone seeking a move-in ready space. The home features 3 bedrooms and 1 modernized bathroom with a brand new tile
shower surround and a stylish vanity. The interior and exterior of the home have been freshly painted, and new flooring
has been installed throughout. The updated kitchen boasts beautiful white shaker-style cabinets with gorgeous granite
countertops, providing ample space for cooking and entertaining. The kitchen also features Samsung stainless steel
appliances, adding to the sleek and modern look. Additionally, the home comes with a convenient garage for parking or
storage. Overall, this beautifully updated ranch-style home is a must see for anyone looking for a move-in ready property that blends style, comfort, and convenience. Property being sold as-is.
